benefits: ['The clean and sturdy design with several well-thought-out details gives TÄLLÅSEN upholstered bed frame a modern look – easy to combine with other bedroom furniture.', 'The headboard cover can be easily removed, machine washed and put back on again, so you can always keep it clean and fresh.', 'The padded headboard is beautiful to look at and comfortable to lean against while reading or watching TV in bed.', 'The soft grey-green Kulsta fabric with a striped pattern adds character to the bed, while the powder-coated parts are color coordinated with the fabric to match each other.', 'The legs are placed on the outer side of the bed frame, adding to the cool and modern look.', 'Adjustable bed sides allow you to use mattresses of different thicknesses.', 'There is plenty of room under the bed for storage boxes, perfect when you want to maximise the use of the space.', 'You can easily vacuum under the bed frame to keep the space clean and dust-free.', 'Pocket springs that respond independently without transferring motion to others.']
longBenefits: {'subject': 'Designer thoughts', 'header': 'Designer Jonas Hultqvist', 'name': 'TÄLLÅSEN Designer Thoughts Sign', 'text': '"My idea with TÄLLÅSEN was to make an upholstered bed frame that stands out in a playful way through the choice of materials, colors and construction. While it has its own expression, it also offers lots of functionality. An example is the padded headboard, which is nice to lean against when sitting up in bed, but also has a subtle print that gives the textile a richer look and texture. So, I hope that many people appreciate both the comfort and the character of TÄLLÅSEN."'}
benefitSummary: Clean lines, color-coordinated upholstery, metal parts and a soft, comfy headboard. TÄLLÅSEN has many well-designed details, adding a modern look to your bedroom that combines easily with other furniture.

longBenefits: {'subject': 'Designer thoughts', 'header': 'Designer Jonas Hultqvist', 'name': 'TÄLLÅSEN Designer Thoughts Sign', 'text': '"My idea with TÄLLÅSEN was to make an upholstered bed frame that stands out in a playful way through the choice of materials, colors and construction. care_instruction: The best way to extend the life of your wooden outdoor furniture is by cleaning it regularly and not leaving it outdoors unprotected more than necessary. Clean: Use a mild soapy solution. Wipe dry with a clean dry cloth. Maintenance: To prevent the surface from drying out and cracking, and moisture from penetrating into the wood, we recommend you to re-stain the furniture on a regular basis, for example once or twice a year. Storing: If possible, store in a cool dry place indoors. If the furniture is stored outside, cover it with a waterproof cover. After a rain or snowfall, wipe off excess water or snow from flat surfaces. Allow air to circulate to avoid condensation. To increase the stability of your furniture, re-tighten the screws at least once per season.

benefits: ['The curved headboard is great for cozy, cocooning moments, helping you to unwind and relax in bed.', 'The headboard is comfortable to lean against ⎼ ideal for lazy mornings in bed drinking coffee and reading.', 'The upholstery has a perfect fit all around the bed, making it pleasing to look at from all angles and great to position in the center of a room.', 'The shaped metal legs are strong and stable and add to the bed´s character.', 'There’s plenty of space under the bed for storage boxes - perfect for storing extra duvets and pillows.', 'You can easily vacuum under the bed frame to keep the space clean and dust-free.', 'Adjustable bed sides allow you to use mattresses of different thicknesses.', 'LURÖY slatted bed base with curved slats helps to absorb your body weight and supports your body, while the open construction allows air to circulate and keeps the mattress fresh.', 'Tallmyra is a hardwearing chenille cover made of 100 percent recycled cotton and polyester and has a soft surface and slightly reflective lustre.']
longBenefits: {'subject': 'Designer thoughts', 'header': 'Designer Ola Wihlborg', 'name': 'TUFJORD designer thought', 'text': '“When I designed TUFJORD, I wanted to maximize comfort and softness and create an embracing feeling in bed. I hope that TUFJORD will be a favorite place in your home, making life more enjoyable both day and night."'}

benefits: ['This upholstered bed frame adds a touch of softness to your bedroom – bringing comfort during the night, and adding style around the clock.', 'The entire cover is removable and machine washable, making your bed easy to keep clean and use for a long time. The cover comes in two pieces, so it’s easy to remove and put back on.', 'The bed frame has timeless look with soft upholstery, a gently curved headboard and piped edges on the headboard and footboard.', 'The bed skirt adds to the look and hides away things that you store under the bed – a perfect space for storage boxes or bulky items.', 'The Klovsta fabric with a distinctive texture is made from at least 90 percent recycled polyester and the grey-white striped pattern gives the bed a vibrant expression.', 'The soft, padded headboard is comfortable to lean against while reading or watching TV in bed.', 'You can easily vacuum under the bed frame to keep the space clean and dust-free.', 'LURÖY slatted bed base with curved slats helps to absorb your body weight and supports your body, while the open construction allows air to circulate and keeps the mattress fresh.']

benefits: ['A statement piece for your dining area with fine details like solid wood edges, breadboard ends with cross-grain pattern and smooth, rounded corners.', 'The round shape of the table makes it great for socializing since everyone can see each other.', 'Self-storing butterfly extension leaf. longBenefits: {'subject': 'Product story summary', 'header': 'A timeless dining experience', 'name': 'SKANSNÄS_Product_story_summary', 'text': 'The 1950s and 60s were a real golden age in Scandinavian design history. benefits: ['Whether you prefer a classically romantic style or a modern and bold one, your existing bed textiles and bedroom furniture will go perfectly with this bed frame.', 'Discrete yet distinctive details on the headboard, footboard and legs give the classic design a unique twist.', 'The white powder-coated steel frame is not only strong and sturdy, but also easy to maintain.', 'You can choose the mattress comfort that’s best for you – the high headboard and footboard work well with mattresses of different thicknesses.', 'You can sit up comfortably in bed thanks to the high headboard – just prop some pillows behind your back and you will have a comfortable place to read or watch TV.', 'The high footboard keeps bed textiles from falling onto the floor while you sleep.', 'There is plenty of room under the bed for storage boxes. Perfect when you want to make the most of your space.', 'You can easily vacuum under the bed frame to keep the space clean and dust-free.', 'LÖNSET slatted bed base with curved slats and comfort zones helps keep your spine aligned, while the open construction allows air to circulate and keeps the mattress fresh.']
longBenefits: {'subject': 'Designer thoughts', 'header': 'Designer Ebba Strandmark', 'name': 'STJÄRNÖ_Ebba Strandmark_Long', 'text': '"When designing STJÄRNÖ bed, the goal was to capture the nostalgic feel of classic, vintage metal furniture. It\'s crafted for a good night\'s sleep, sweet dreams and beautiful bedding."'}

benefits: ['Timeless design with soft rounded corners and a scratch-resistant surface mean that the bed will last for many years.', 'You can easily change the look of the bed by choosing a headboard in a different color.', 'The bed grows with your child, but still keeps its proportions thanks to the clever design of the side panels.', 'With a guard rail on the side of the bed, you can reduce the risk of your child falling out of bed.', 'The guard rail is simple to fix in place and remove – without leaving marks on the side of the bed.', 'You do not need to keep track of the parts needed to extend the bed since they are included and mounted on the frame.', 'The headboard is easily mounted to SLÄKT extendable bed frame.', 'If you like the style, you can combine the bed with other matching pieces of furniture in the SLÄKT and SMÅSTAD series.', 'The slatted bed base lies firmly in place thanks to hooks that you fix to the bed frame.', 'The curved slats with a springy feel adjust to your body weight and create a supple foundation for the mattress.', 'The slats are spaced to offer good support for both spring and foam mattresses.']
longBenefits: {'subject': 'Form/Design process', 'header': 'Created together with children', 'name': 'Collaboration with children', 'text': 'Children are the most important people in the world and we’re curious to hear what they have to say since we create products for them! Therefore, we invite children to creative and playful sessions where they get to participate in our product development. Here they can express themselves freely and draw, show or tell us what is important to them. Their opinions matter and make our products better. After all, they’re the experts!'}
benefitSummary: A bed that grows with your child – in length and in style. You simply pull out the bed and replace the headboard when you want to change the expression. And an included guard rail protects your child.

benefits: ['Part of the Nytillverkad collection where several IKEA classics have been given a new look.', 'Designer Noboru Nakamura used LAPPMON sofa as a starting point and shortened it by 18 centimeters to make the covers for KLIPPAN washable – a width that suited fabric reels and washing machines.', 'Hallsta cover was first shown on the cover of our 1984 catalogue. Now, 40 years later, it has been given a new life under the name Långban.', 'Durable metal springs in the seat give the sofa a springy comfort, allowing you to sit, relax and enjoy it for many years.', '10-year limited warranty. Read about the terms in the limited warranty brochure.']
longBenefits: {'subject': 'Form/Design process', 'header': 'A sofa for the many people', 'name': 'KLIPPAN Nytillverkad', 'text': 'In the late 1970s, product developer Lars Engman asked designer Noboru Nakamura to create a robust sofa with soft corners and a washable cover – at a price that families with small children could afford. Nakamura used LAPPMON sofa as a starting point. By simplifying and shortening it by 3 inches, less material was required – and there was room for more on each pallet. KLIPPAN sofa was born and introduced in 1980.'}
benefitSummary: KLIPPAN was introduced in 1980 and grew in popularity over the years. With its clean-lined look, kid-friendly corners and washable covers, it has now been a top seller for almost half a century!

benefits: ['The anthracite powder-coated steel frame is not only strong and sturdy, but also easy to maintain.', 'Discrete yet distinctive details on the headboard, footboard and legs give the classic design a unique twist.', 'Whether you prefer a classically romantic style or a modern and bold one, your existing bed textiles and bedroom furniture will go perfectly with this bed frame.', 'LYNGÖR mattress base has flat slats for an even and uniform foundation for the mattress.', 'Easy to get in and out of bed because the mattress base makes the bed higher.', 'Easy to keep clean since the mattress base cover can be removed and machine washed.', 'You can sit up comfortably in bed thanks to the high headboard – just prop some pillows behind your back and you will have a comfortable place to read or watch TV.', 'There is plenty of room under the bed for storage boxes. Perfect when you want to make the most of your space.']
longBenefits: {'subject': 'Designer thoughts', 'header': 'Designer Ebba Strandmark', 'name': 'STJÄRNÖ_Ebba Strandmark_Long', 'text': '"When designing STJÄRNÖ bed, the goal was to capture the nostalgic feel of classic, vintage metal furniture. My idea was to convey a warm and traditional charm combined with a cool aura. This bed suits many different styles and materials, inspiring the creation of inviting and harmonic bedrooms with a cosy atmosphere. It\'s crafted for a good night\'s sleep, sweet dreams and beautiful bedding."'}
benefitSummary: STJÄRNÖ is a classic bed frame with decorative details that add a twist to the steel design – and LYNGÖR mattress base gives extra height and helps your mattress keep its shape for longer.

Clean: Use a mild soapy solution. Wipe dry with a clean dry cloth. Maintenance: To prevent the surface from drying out and cracking, and moisture from penetrating into the wood, we recommend you to re-stain the furniture on a regular basis, for example once or twice a year. Storing: If possible, store in a cool dry place indoors. If the furniture is stored outside, cover it with a waterproof cover. After a rain or snowfall, wipe off excess water or snow from flat surfaces. Allow air to circulate to avoid condensation. To increase the stability of your furniture, re-tighten the screws at least once per season.

benefits: ['This 4-seat table can easily be extended into a 6-seat table using the included self-storing leaf.', 'The self-storing leaf is easy to insert to extend the table and just as easy to remove and tuck away under the table top when your guests have gone home.', 'The round shape of the table makes it great for socializing since everyone can see each other.', 'Thanks to new research and a new technique, the upholstered chair gives you optimal seating comfort. Change the style anytime by replacing the chair cover with one in a different color or model.', 'The upholstery of the chair consists of straight polyester fibers with small gaps between them – providing comfy elasticity and better ventilation so you enjoy a pleasant temperature when sitting.', "The seat's bowl-shaped bottom is adapted for your sit bones and those of most of the world's population. And with an innovative technique, the seat's padding is shaped to maximize your comfort.", 'The chair cover is easy to keep clean as it is removable and can be machine washed.', 'The backrest has a built-in lumbar support and the angle between the seat and the backrest is optimally adapted to make it comfortable for you to sit a little longer at the dining table.', 'The chair cover comes in one piece and fixes in place with hook-and-loop fasteners so you can easily pull it off and put it back on again.', 'The chair legs are made of solid wood, which is a durable natural material.']

longBenefits: {'subject': 'Function/solution', 'header': '"Ketchup or mustard?"', 'name': 'KORVBRÖD - PL', 'text': "Long, thin sausages served in hot-dog buns are the classic Swedish fast food, and if ever visiting Sweden, you'll find small hot-dog stands all over. With KORV (wiener sausage) and KORVBRÖD (hot dog bread) you can make your own hot-dogs at home. Ketchup and mustard, such as KETCHUP (tomato ketchup) and SENAP MILD (mild mustard), are the traditional toppings, but ROSTAD LÖK (roasted onion) is also very popular. Simmer or fry the sausages - done!"}

longBenefits: {'subject': 'Material', 'header': 'What is stainless steel?', 'name': 'What is stainless steel_general/cross-HFB text', 'text': 'Stainless steel is found in everything from building structures and cars to sinks and knives. longBenefits: {'subject': 'Material', 'header': 'What is mirror glass?', 'name': 'What is mirror glass_general/cross-HFB text', 'text': 'Mirror glass is made of mostly of ordinary glass with a reflective coating in some kind of metal. In the past it was common for the coating to contain lead or mercury – but over time, both of these metals have been shown to be harmful to people and the environment. That’s why, as of several years ago, IKEA has a total ban on using lead or mercury in our mirrors and instead it is non-toxic silver or aluminium that reflects your mirror image.'}
